      public SpaceMarine(String name, Coordinates coordinates, Double health, AstartesCategory category, Weapon weaponType, MeleeWeapon meleeWeapon, Chapter chapter, CollectionManager collectionManager)
      builds new object and generate id and current date as date of creation
      Parameters:
      name - name of the space marine (cannot be null)
      coordinates - coordinates of the space marine
      health - health of the space marine (can be null or must be greater than 0)
      category - astartes category of the space marine (cannot be null)
      weaponType - weapon type of the space marine (cannot be null)
      meleeWeapon - melee weapon type of the space marine (can be null)
      chapter - chapter of the space marine
      collectionManager - needs for generation id
